<body>
  <section class="hero is-fullheight is-default is-bold">
    <% include ../partials/header %>
    <div class="hero-body">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="columns is-multiline">
          <div class="column is-8 is-offset-2">
            <div class="level">
              <div class="level-left">
                <div class="level-item">
                  <div class="title is-3">
                    Gotta Go!
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="level-right">
                <div class="level-item">
                  <a class="button" href="https://gotta-go.herokuapp.com/">Check it out live</a>
                  <a class="button" href="https://github.com/mford008/gotta-go-react">Source code</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="column is-8 is-offset-2">
            <div class="title is-5">
              The Problem:
            </div>
            <div class="">
              <p>
                Everyone has "gotta go" at one point or another. Drivers, especially
                those providing rides for others through ride-sharing apps, can end
                up in a place they don't always recognize. We found a lack of information
                online about the locations of bathrooms, even in large cities like San Francisco.
              </p>
            </div>
            <br />
            <div class="title is-5">
              The Solution:
            </div>
            <div class="">
              <p>
                Gotta Go aims to solve that problem by crowdsourcing information about
                restrooms and pit stops by people who are actually using them.
                Our app allows users to see all the locations of restrooms input by
                other users, and allows them to add new locations themselves.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- <div class="column is-4 is-offset-1">
