          <div class="column is-8 is-offset-2">
            <p>
              We originally created the app using HTML with EJS templating, Bulma for
              styling, and MySQL to store information including location, comments,
              and user login information.
            </p>
            <br />
            <p>
              After some time, we decided to refactor our codebase, using React for
              the frontend, and MongoDB for less restrictive data handling.
            </p>
          </div>
          <!-- <div class="column is-4 is-offset-4">
            <figure class="image">
